REF.: 
  - G. C. Abell, Phys. Rev. B31, 6184 (1985).
  - B. W. Dodson, Phys. Rev. B35, 2795 (1987).
  - J. Tersoff, Phys. Rev. B39, 5566 (1989).
  -    Y. Kawazoe, M. Mikami, K. Ohno, "COMPUTER SIMULATION NI-YORU
       BUSSITSU-KAGAKU", (Japanese), KYOURITSU-SYUPPAN, P.75, (1996).
